These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, nurse, paramedic, pilot, security-guard
House: art-deco, farmhouse, modern, ranch-style, craftsman, colonial
 1. the modern house is on the left of the lawyer##1
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 3. the manager is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 4. the colonial house is not to the left of the nurse##8
 5. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 6. the craftsman house is somewhere between the modern house and the security-guard##7
 7. the lawyer is not to the left of the modern house##8
 8. the pilot is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left or right of the pilot##3
10. the art-deco house is not to the left of the paramedic##8
11. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
12. the manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
13. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
14. the security-guard is somewhere between the farmhouse house and the nurse##7
15. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
16. the pilot is not the ranch-style house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Job           | paramedic | manager | lawyer | pilot | security-guard | nurse |
| House   | art-deco | modern    | farmhouse  | craftsman  | ranch-style            | colonial  |

