.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, photography, puzzles, sudoku, woodworking
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, drama, action, romance, western
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person watching western movies##6
 2. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person watching western movies is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 6. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
 7. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person watching action movies##6
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person watching drama movies##8
12. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
13. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
15. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Hobby   | photography | woodworking | magic-tricks | sudoku | puzzles | cooking |
| Movie-Genre     | drama  | comedy  | martial-arts         | western | romance    | action   |

