.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  police-officer, security-guard, accountant, photographer, teacher, project-manager
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, cricket, sailing, soccer, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
 2. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the security-guard##8
 5. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 6. the project-manager is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
 8. the photographer is not to the right of the photographer##8
 9. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the teacher and the person who's sport is cricket##7
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
13. the project-manager is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
14. the security-guard is on the right of the photographer##1
15. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the police-officer##7
16. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
17. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
18. the teacher is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
19. the person who's sport is cricket is not the police-officer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| Job   | teacher   | accountant | project-manager    | photographer      | security-guard | police-officer |
| Sport         | biathlon | soccer  | basketball | weightlifting | cricket   | sailing  |

