.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
There 6 different types of food: eggplant, pineapple, pomegranate, radish, tomato, zucchini
City: miami, hamburg, boston, san-francisco, new-york, berlin
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
 2. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 3. the person eating zucchini is between the person traveling to miami and the person eating eggplant##2
 4. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person traveling to hamburg##7
 6. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 8. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
10. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
11. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
12. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person eating zucchini##7
13. the person traveling to berlin is not to the right of the person traveling to boston##8
14. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
15. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
16. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
17. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Food    | eggplant | zucchini    | tomato     | radish  | pineapple    | pomegranate |
| City   | hamburg  | new-york | miami | berlin | boston | san-francisco     |

