 7. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 8. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
10. the owner of the horse is not the person drinking juice##6
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
13. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | fanta | lemonade  | soy-milk     | water | juice |
| Pet           | cat        | goat    | turtle | chinchilla | horse     | hamster  |

